{"TopicId":177240,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[1.6.x] Kerbal heatshield","CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-02T06:32:17Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-02T06:32:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYAY, this is my first mod. Thanks to people who supported me, and \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/50907-spannermonkeysmce/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002250907\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/50907-spannermonkeysmce/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SpannerMonkey(smce)\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0for teaching me how to mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter years of investment and R\u0026amp;D, this is what we come up with. A golf-ball looking heatshield for kerbals.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHOW TO USE:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. get it in your inventory.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. get into a suborbital trajectory.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. Equip the heatshield.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4. BURNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNNN\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA simple demonstration, by kottabosgames:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/GCFeXgIayeg?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5. deploy personal parasail, wait for full deployment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n6. once you have full deployment, DIVE and pull up to get yourself flying\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n7. Land.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDEPENDENCIES: \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E and all its dependencies:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1214304498\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/149848-14-kerbal-inventory-system-kis-v114/\u0026amp;tab=comments\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=2801128\u0026amp;embedComment=2801128\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment#comment-2801128\u0022 style=\u0022height:329px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDownload: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/1925/Kerbal%20heatshield\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://spacedock.info/mod/1925/Kerbal heatshield\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLicense:\u00A0CC-BY-SA 2.0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E is supported.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInstall instructions: copy the \u0022kerbal heatshield\u0022 file in the .zip to your gamedata file.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQ\u0026amp;A\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. IS XDTHEGREAT NUTS?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, I am a human.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Will you do more stupid stuff like this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYES. GIVE ME IDEAS.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. Is there more stupid stuff I can do with this mod?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. Use your imagination!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4. Why does the heatshield look like a golf\u00A0ball?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is what our XD team developed, and is totally not because I am a noob and is lazy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5. Why should I choose this mod?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPrevent kerbals from burning up collecting eva reports in the upper atmosphere, and can incinerate kerbals without risking them die. Or uninstalling the mod and let them pop.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDISCLAIMER: I DO NOT TAKE ANY RESPONSIBILITIES FOR EYE OR MENTAL DAMAGE DUE TO THE UGLY GRAPHICS AND CRAZY IDEAS.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nENJOY.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-02-04T10:46:31Z\u0022 title=\u002202/04/2019 10:46  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 4, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Xd the great\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"hab136","CreatedById":75997,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-02T13:36:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\npics?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-03T03:04:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223426443\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022177240\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221533216997\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002275997\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022hab136\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, hab136 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\npics?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe. Too lazy for that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts just a red golfball. Who needs pics?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kurgut","CreatedById":188918,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-08-03T08:52:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-co